@NODE "Information" "Black Horizon Campaign"
@{JCENTER} @{b} @{UU} Information
@{PLAIN}
@{JLEFT}
This campaign is designed for AVERAGE
(completed Main campaign on Medium skill)
to EXPERT players (completed Main Campaign
on Hard or Insane) and is designed to be
fairly hard.
NOVICE players should look elsewhere.
Freespace Campaign designed from scratch
Missions 2 and 10 are not completeable on
hard. Mission 4 is not completable in
single player, but it makes for great
multiplayer.
Do NOT save over these files if you
intend on changing them (use a diff. file
name).




* Play Information *

Max Number of players:
1 in single player, 4 or 9 in multi
(depends on mission)

Team/Coop:
Three co-op missions.

New Sounds:
Yes, some new voice over effects like
message beeps.  Nothing really exciting

New Graphics:
No

Other Stuff:
This campaign does NOT modify the ship or
weapon tree files




* Construction *
Base of construction:
All missions designed from scratch

Editor(s) used:
FRED, wordpad, sound recorder, Midisoft
Pro Wav editor

Extractors used:
VPView

Known Bugs:
NONE (i hope)!  Maybe some grammer erros
or spelling, but nothing major!
@ENDNODE

